# Notes reprise

## UI

Monter composer up
attendre génération (30m +)

## BDD
Restore sans table histo
4Go zippée ou 40Go+ dézippée



```
docker compose up

docker cp /opt/mongodb-2026-03-04_093723.gzip catalogue_apprentissage_mongodb:/opt/mongodb-2026-03-04_093723.gzip

docker exec -it catalogue_apprentissage_mongodb bash

mongorestore --drop --gzip --archive=/opt/mongodb-2026-03-04_093723.gzip --nsExclude="catalogue-apprentissage.histories"

docker compose down
```
